            </nav>

            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="https://github.com/RothC0L" target="_blank" class="social-link">
                    <i class="bi bi-github"></i>
                </a>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/picha-patraneramit/" target="_blank" class="social-link">
                    <i class="bi bi-linkedin"></i>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </aside>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="main-content">
        <!-- About Section -->
        <section id="about" class="content-section">
            <div class="section-content">
                <div class="about-container">
                    <div class="about-image">
                        <img src="image/me.jpg" alt="Picha Patraneramit" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="about-text">
                        <p class="mb-4">
                            Full Stack Developer with 2+ years of experience building enterprise web, mobile, and kiosk systems using C#, .NET, SQL Server, and RESTful APIs.
                            Experienced in large-scale API design, system modernization, and secure payment and hardware integration, with strong end-to-end delivery
                            and a Master's focus in Cybersecurity, including a thesis on penetration testing and OWASP-based vulnerability mitigation.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Experience Section -->
        <section id="experience" class="content-section">
            <div class="section-content">
                <div class="experience-item">
                    <div class="timeline">Mar 2024 — PRESENT</div>
                    <div class="experience-content">
                        <h3 class="experience-title">
                            Full-Stack Developer, meeSoft Co, Ltd.
                            @* <i class="bi bi-arrow-up-right ms-2"></i> *@
                        </h3>
                        <ul class="experience-description custom-bullets">
                            <li>Designed and deployed 39+ RESTful API endpoints to support extensive building management features and user services for a large-scale public community mobile application.</li>
                            <li>Developed 5 core RESTful API endpoints using C# & LINQ for Smart Locker system, enhancing secure package handling for a premium residential condominium.</li>
                            <li>Led the migration of a legacy mobile application from Xamarin to .NET MAUI, restoring availability on the Google Play Store and ensuring full compatibility with the latest Android OS, while reducing long-term maintenance risks.</li>
                            <li>Engineered specialized libraries to connect EDC hardware with 2 Major Thai Banks and 1 International Bank, alongside integrating third-party payment gateways for secure web transactions.</li>
                            <li>Managed the Access Control System for a top-ranked university in Thailand, overseeing hardware configuration (Board IPs/Security Zones) and implementing granular user permission protocols.</li>
                            <li>Built and deployed an Automated Server Monitoring Service with real-time API tracking and SMTP alerts, significantly reducing system downtime.</li>
                            <li>Developed an Automated Cleanup Bot for server storage management, including pre-and-post disk space analysis and automated reporting, reducing manual maintenance by 90%.</li>
                            <li>Led end-to-end development and implementation of an interactive kiosk system for a world-class indoor playground in Thailand, using Unity, C# for an interactive front-end and C# with RESTful APIs, LINQ, and SQL Server for backend services and data management.</li>
                        </ul>
                        <div class="tech-tags">
                            <span class="tech-tag">C# .NET</span>
                            <span class="tech-tag">LINQ</span>
                            <span class="tech-tag">SQL Server</span>
                            <span class="tech-tag">.NET MAUI</span>
                            <span class="tech-tag">Unity Game Engine</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="experience-item">
                    <div class="timeline">Nov 2023 - Feb 2024</div>
                    <div class="experience-content">
                        <h3 class="experience-title">
                            .NET Developer, PRO BIZ SOFT Co., Ltd.
                            @* <i class="bi bi-arrow-up-right ms-2"></i> *@
                        </h3>
                        <ul class="experience-description custom-bullets">
                            <li>Developed and maintained front-end web applications using C#.NET, React, TypeScript, Node.js, HTML, and CSS to support business operations and implemented responsive, UX/UI-compliant user interactions and interfaces.</li>
                            <li>Troubleshot and resolved application issues to ensure stability and performance.</li>
                        </ul>
                        <div class="tech-tags">
                            <span class="tech-tag">ReactTS</span>
                            <span class="tech-tag">Typescript</span>
                            <span class="tech-tag">C#</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <a href="doc/resume.pdf" class="view-resume" target="_blank">
                    View Full Resume <i class="bi bi-arrow-right ms-2"></i>
                </a>
